title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: When attempting to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown. The issue occurs specifically when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight or map. This bug report aims to provide the necessary details to reproduce and fix the issue.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown during the export process.
EB: The data should be successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight or map. 
3. Attempt to export the data from the table. 
4. Observe the exception being thrown during the export process.
